	"description": "I was a just another happy college student, double majoring in Computer Science\nand Economics at a university in Egypt.\n\nI had fallen in love with programming after taking a few C++ classes.\n\nI will never forget writing my first for loop and having it execute on screen\nwithout errors on the first try. I will never forget my professor telling me\nthat I have good coding skills, and great potential if I keep it up.\n\nCoding just made sense. Creating something and watching it come to life is the\nmost",
